Have any of been able to read content from the `Developer Info` (in the Sprocket menu) directly in the console?
I would like to be able to quickly look up things like `portal_id` in the console, instead of having to open up the Developer Info and searching for it.

Hi... Is it normal to get automatically logged out of your HubSpot account regularly? Is this some kind of a built-in security settings from HubSpot itself ? Can I get rid of this by tweaking any settings ?

It's really annoying when you have login every single day even though all the cookies, browser history is completely intact...
